description:
Cary is a college student with a very strong entrepreneurial streak. He says he wants to finish college and then begin building his empire.

He's got a tattoo on his back and he said he was very careful not to take it up to his neck, so that it would not be visible once he starts wearing a suit and tie!

He's straight but, unlike most straight guys, wasn't shy at all about showing off his asshole — and a nice one it is!
title: Cary
